3. Stacks.js: The Frontend & Backend SDK

Stacks.js is a collection of JavaScript libraries that enables seamless interaction with the Stacks blockchain from apps, wallets, servers, or browsers.

Capabilities:

Wallet authentication via Hiro Wallet or Leather

Read/write contract calls

Build off-chain microservices

Handle transaction serialization

Work with SIP-010 tokens, NFTs, or custom contracts

If youâ€™re building a web dApp, Stacks.js is essential.
